    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Gérard M. Baudet</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.cs.uri.edu/about-us/people/gerard-baudet/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ae/Gerardbaudet1.jpg/200px-Gerardbaudet1.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"247\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/ae/Gerardbaudet1.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Gerardbaudet1.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Gérard M. Baudet <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Gérard M. Baudet</b>,<br />\na French computer scientist and associate professor at the Department of Computer Science and Statistics, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Rhode_Island\">University of Rhode Island</a>, previously affiliated with the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_Institute_for_Research_in_Computer_Science_and_Automation\">French National Institute for Research in Computer Science and Control (INRIA)</a> \nin <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rocquencourt\">Paris-Rocquencourt</a>. He holds a Ph.D. from <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a> in 1978 on <i>The Design and Analysis of Algorithms for Asynchronous Multiprocessors</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and researched on <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a> and <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1976_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1976 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#1980_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1980 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=G%C3%A9rard_M._Baudet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1976_...\">1976 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=G%C3%A9rard_M._Baudet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1976 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1976</b>). <i>Asynchronous iterative methods for multiprocessors</i>. <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/An-Analysis-of-the-Full-Alpha-Beta-Pruning-Baudet/20e3f9141b7b3db6a346a09a4c47c7a34bae075f\">An Analysis of the Full Alpha-Beta Pruning Algorithm</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/stoc/stoc78.html\">STOC 1978</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0004370278800113\">On the branching factor of the alpha-beta pruning algorithm</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_Intelligence_(journal)\">Artificial Intelligence</a>, Vol. 10</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Asynchronous-Iterative-Methods-for-Multiprocessors-Baudet/aeb50872722ccd2e606640cac1c46b684ed34136\">Asynchronous Iterative Methods for Multiprocessors</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Journal\" title=\"ACM\">Journal of the ACM</a>, Vol. 25, No. 2 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i>The Design and Analysis of Algorithms for Asynchronous Multiprocessors</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, Advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#Kung\" title=\"Mathematician\">Hsiang-Tsung Kung</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1980_...\">1980 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=G%C3%A9rard_M._Baudet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 1980 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#Brent\" title=\"Mathematician\">Richard P. Brent</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#Kung\" title=\"Mathematician\">Hsiang-Tsung Kung</a> (<b>1980</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://wwwmaths.anu.edu.au/~brent/pub/pub058.html\">Parallel Execution of a Sequence of tasks on a Asynchronous Multiprocessor</a></i>. Australian Computer Journal, Vol. 12, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1981</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-68402-9_12\">On the Area Required by VLSI Circuits</a></i>. in <a href=\"/Mathematician#Kung\" title=\"Mathematician\">Hsiang-Tsung Kung</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#BSproull\" title=\"Mathematician\">Bob Sproull</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#GSteele\" title=\"Mathematician\">Guy Steele</a> (eds.) <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/book/10.1007/978-3-642-68402-9\">VLSI Systems and Computations</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Springer_Science%2BBusiness_Media\">Springer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franco_P._Preparata\">Franco P. Preparata</a>, <a href=\"/Mathematician#JVuillemin\" title=\"Mathematician\">Jean Vuillemin</a> (<b>1983</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1676300\">Area-Time Optimal VLSI Circuits for Convolution</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOC\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computers</a>, Vol. 32, No 7</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=G%C3%A9rard_M._Baudet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.cs.uri.edu/about-us/people/gerard-baudet/\">Associate Professor Gerard Baudet</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Rhode_Island\">University of Rhode Island</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=50316\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Gerard Baudet</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=G%C3%A9rard_M._Baudet&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.cs.uri.edu/about-us/people/gerard-baudet/\">Associate Professor Gerard Baudet</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Rhode_Island\">University of Rhode Island</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gérard M. Baudet</a> (<b>1978</b>). <i>The Design and Analysis of Algorithms for Asynchronous Multiprocessors</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Carnegie_Mellon_University\" title=\"Carnegie Mellon University\">Carnegie Mellon University</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#Kung\" title=\"Mathematician\">Hsiang-Tsung Kung</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Baudet:G=eacute=rard_M=\">dblp: Gérard M. Baudet</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://projects.csail.mit.edu/jacm/References/baudet1978:226.html\">Journal of the ACM Bibliography - Gérard M. Baudet</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301150718\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4692-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301150718 and revision id 8677\n -->\n"
